data.description: Experience mountain living at its best, this 3 bedroom 3 bathroom home sits on an acre of partially fenced property. This home boasts  an open floor plan with cathedral style ceilings, saltillo tile floors, new interior and exterior paint, new roof, Freshly abated landscaping and 360 degree views of the Santa Rosa, San Jacinto, and San Gorgonio mountain ranges. This home has it all...room for expansion, room for horses or other farm animals and borders national forest land for the ultimate privacy, the sky is the limit. Come see what the good life looks like and make this mountain home yours. Only 30 mins to Palm Desert, shopping, entertainment, and restaurants.
